metadata.description: By owning this NFT you will have access to and become a member of the cult of bunny - This collection of bunnies is built on the Etherium blockchain. Owning a bunny offers you access to the cults community which has its own benefits. Future perks including carrots will become available through the roadmap. Visit https://www.bunnydeathcult.com for more details
